\begin{alertblock}{\textbf{CONCLUSION}}
The propose system could resolve the interpersonal communication problem between signers and hearing community by building up a new communication bridge with the Kinect and Leap Motion integration for applications in ASL FOR automatic translation, such as ASL to text processing.\newline  
\textbf{FUTURE WORK:}
\begin{itemize}
\item Improve Accuracy
\item Integrate Text-To-Audio Translation
\item Integrate Text-To- 3D ASL Animation
\end{itemize}

\end{alertblock}


